 2003-14632003-09-30,  ,  ,  ,  LAB
ActCanada Labour Code
PrecisAppointment of LOUISE FECTEAU of Outremont, Quebec, to be a Vice-Chairperson of the Canada Industrial Relations Board, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of four years; order that LOUISE FECTEAU be deemed to be employed in the Public Service for the purposes of the Public Service Superannuation Act; and determine that LOUISE FECTEAU shall reside within 210 kilometres of the National Capital Region; effective October 1, 2003.
